quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  15,80,Hijr ke log bhi Rasoolon ki takzeeb kar chuke hain
  15,81,"Humne apni aayat unke paas bheji, apni nishaniyan unko dikhayi, magar woh sabko nazar-andaz (ignore) hi karte rahey"
  15,82,Woh pahad tarash tarash kar makaan banate thay aur apni jagah bilkul be-khauf aur mutmaeen thay
  15,83,Aakhir e kaar ek zabardast dhamake ne unko subah hotey hi aa liya
  15,84,Aur unki kamayi unke kuch kaam na aayi
  15,85,"Humne zameen aur aasman ko aur unki sab maujoodaat ko haqq ke siwa kisi aur buniyaad par khalq (create) nahin kiya hai, aur faisle ki ghadi yaqeenan aane wali hai. Pas (aey Muhammad), tum (in logon ki behudgiyon par) shareefana darguzar se kaam lo"
  15,86,Yaqeenan tumahra Rubb sab ka khaliq hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai
  15,87,"Humne tumko saat (seven) aisi aayatein de rakkhi hain jo baar baar dohrayi janey ke layiq hain, aur tumhein Quran e azeem ata kiya hai"
  15,88,"Tum us mata-e-duniya ki taraf aankh utha kar na dekho jo humne in mein se mukhtalif qisam ke logon ko de rakkhi hai, aur na inke haal par apna dil kudhao(grieve), inhein chodh kar iman laney walon ki taraf jhuko"
  15,89,Aur (na maanne walon se) kehdo ke main to saaf saaf tambeeh(warn) karne wala hoon
  15,90,Yeh usi ki tarah ki tambeeh hai jaisi humne un tafarraqe pardazon(those who make division) ki taraf bheji thi
  15,91,Jinhon ne apne Quran ko tukde tukde kar dala hai
  15,92,"To kasam hai tere Rubb ki, hum zaroor in sabse puchenge"
  15,93,Ke tum kya karte rahey ho
  15,94,Pas (aey Nabi) jis cheez ka tumhein hukum diya jaa raha hai usey hankey pukare kehdo(proclaim publicly) aur shirk karne walon ki zara parwah na karo
  15,95,Tumhari taraf se hum un mazaaq udane walon ki khabar lenay ke liye kafi hain
  15,96,Jo Allah ke saath kisi aur ko bhi khuda qarar dete hain anqareeb unhein maloom ho jayega
  15,97,Humein maloom hai ke jo baatein yeh log tumpar banate hain unsey tumhare dil ko sakht koft hoti hai (heart is distressed)
  15,98,"Iska ilaaj yeh hai ke apne Rubb ki hamd ke saath uski tasbeeh karo, uski janaab mein sajda baja lao"
  15,99,Aur us aakhri ghadi tak apne Rubb ki bandagi karte raho jiska aana yaqeeni hai